  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
      <section class="report__action">
        <header>
          <h1 class="title title--section">Action</h1>
        </header>
         <ul class="cards">
          <li class="card card--action">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="large-2 columns">
                <span class="action__date">12/07</span>
              </div>
              <div class="large-10 columns">
                <p class="card__content">I didn't get a chance to workout today and It made me feel guilty, and kind of lazy.</p>
                <p class="card__content card__content--solution">I'm going to wake up early tomorrow and go for a 30 minute run.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="card card--action">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="large-2 columns">
                <span class="action__date">12/06</span>
              </div>
              <div class="large-10 columns">
                <p class="card__content ">I spent $70 today on eating out.</p>
                <p class="card__content card__content--solution">I have to find time to make at least one of my meals everyday this week.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="card card--action">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="large-2 columns">
                <span class="action__date">12/05</span>
              </div>
              <div class="large-10 columns">
                <p class="card__content ">I didn't finish my weekly report on time.</p>
                <p class="card__content card__content--solution">I will stop over-committing my time so I have time for the important things.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="card card--action">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="large-2 columns">
                <span class="action__date">12/04</span>
              </div>
              <div class="large-10 columns">
                <p class="card__content"> I ate a lot of junk food for lunch.</p>
                <p class="card__content card__content--solution">I will pack my meal and snacks the night before so I don't get so hungry when I get busy at work. I'll also leave some healthy snacks in my desk. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="card card--action">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="large-2 columns">
                <span class="action__date">12/03</span>
              </div>
              <div class="large-10 columns">
                <p class="card__content"> I yelled at my mom for ruining my sweater in the wash.</p>
                <p class="card__content card__content--solution">I'll keep my delicate clothes separate and be more empathetic - she was just trying to help!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>

        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
